    "Rex learns change rules that capture dependencies between different regions of code or configuration, based on patterns observed in commit logs spanning several months.",
    "When an engineer modifies a subset of files within a change rule, Rex suggests additional changes to ensure consistency and completeness.",
    "The tool has been effectively implemented within services such as Office 365 and Azure, impacting over 5,000 changes in the system.On the other hand, issue-report-to-fix-commit links are critical for security, aiding in understanding code changes and assessing security implications.",
    "In particular, establishing robust links between issues and fixes helps in tracking which code changes address specific vulnerabilities or bugs.",
    "This traceability ensures that identified issues are addressed systematically and that fixes are correctly applied, which is essential for maintaining security [108]."
